Eviction is a process of invalidating cachelines in order to map to a new addresses

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
title: Eviction priorities
id: priorities
---

The product shall perfrom eviction based on the priority information
associated with IO classes.

The product shall evict in the following order:

1. IO classes with excedeed occupancy limit.
2. Lower priority IO classes (omit pinned IO Classes)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
title: Cold data eviction
id: cold
---

The product shall evict the data within a single IO class in the last recently
used (LRU) order.
